OL,3,CProgress and uncertainty around public
OL,4,Csector pay deals
OL,6,FAfter progress in recent days, there
OL,7,Fis now a pay deal on the table for
OL,8,Fhealth workers, public transport
OL,9,Fstaff, and the majority of civil
OL,10,Fservants.
OL,12,FDepartments are offering a 5% pay rise
OL,13,Fwith a #1500 ''one-off payment''.
OL,15,FThe pay deals will now be put to union
OL,16,Fmembers, but some unions believe the
OL,17,Fdeals still fall short.
