OL,3,CProgress and uncertainty around public
OL,4,Csector pay deals
OL,6,FIn the health sector, under the
OL,7,Fproposed settlement thousands of
OL,8,Fhealth workers will have pay parity
OL,9,Frestored on their pay bands, and will
OL,10,Ffurther receive an unconsolidated lump
OL,11,Fsum for all staff on Agenda for Change
OL,12,Fterms and conditions.
OL,14,FThe offer will be backdated to April
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FUnions will now put the offer to their
OL,18,Fmembers, but the Royal College of
OL,19,FNursing say the deal still falls short.
