OL,6,FRita Devlin of the RCN NI said that
OL,7,Fshe wouldn't be making a
OL,8,Frecommendation to their members as to
OL,9,Fhow to vote.
OL,11,FShe said members would be given all
OL,12,Fthe information they need to
OL,13,Funderstand a complicated pay offer.
OL,15,FSpeaking to UTV, she said there were
OL,16,Fconcerns over the one-off lump sum,
OL,17,Fand how it may disadvantage some
OL,18,Fmembers.
