OL,6,FThere has been progress as well for
OL,7,Ftransport workers. Three days of
OL,8,Findustrial action scheduled for later
OL,9,Fthis week has been called off after
OL,10,Funions received a new offer.
OL,12,FIt comes after Unite, GMB and Siptu
OL,13,Freconvened talks with Translink on
OL,14,FSunday.
OL,16,FThe three unions are to ballot their
OL,17,Fmembers on the new offer.
