OL,6,FMeanwhile, Civil servants in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have been made an offer of a
OL,8,F5% pay increase and a one-off #1,500
OL,9,Fpayment.
OL,11,FStormont Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,12,FArchibald put forward the offer on
OL,13,FMonday.
