OL,3,CProgress and uncertainty around public
OL,4,Csector pay deals
OL,6,FThe offer includes a 5% increase to
OL,7,Fthe majority of Civil Service pay
OL,8,Fscales, bringing up the pay of the
OL,9,Flowest-paid staff to the voluntary
OL,10,FLiving Wage Foundation rates of #12 an
OL,11,Fhour or #23,177 annually ` a 10%
OL,12,Fincrease ` performance-related
OL,13,Fprogression and a #1,500 non-
OL,14,Fconsolidated payment to staff eligible
OL,15,Ffor the 2023 pay award.
OL,17,FIt comes following negotiations with
OL,18,FCivil Service trade unions.
OL,20,FThose unions too are now set to confer
OL,21,Fwith their members over the offer.
