OL,3,CProgress and uncertainty around public
OL,4,Csector pay deals
OL,6,FFollowing the restoration of devolved
OL,7,Fgovernment earlier this month, Ms
OL,8,FArchibald said her department aimed to
OL,9,Fmove quickly.
OL,11,F"Following meetings with recognised
OL,12,FCivil Service unions last week, I am
OL,13,Fpleased to have been able to move
OL,14,Fquickly to make this pay offer for
OL,15,Fcivil servants which recognises their
OL,16,Frole in the delivery of public
OL,17,Fservices," she said.
