OL,3,CProgress and uncertainty around public
OL,4,Csector pay deals
OL,6,F"Civil servants, like other public
OL,7,Fservants, have been waiting some time
OL,8,Ffor their 2023 pay award against the
OL,9,Fcontext of a cost-of-living crisis and
OL,10,Fpressures on their own household
OL,11,Fbudgets.
OL,13,F"I hope staff will look favourably on
OL,14,Fthe offer and that unions'
OL,15,Fconsultation with their members will
OL,16,Fproceed as swiftly as possible so we
OL,17,Fcan get pay to staff as soon as
OL,18,Fpracticable.
