OL,6,F"Our public sector workers are at the
OL,7,Fheart of service delivery. We have a
OL,8,Fchallenging journey of enhancing
OL,9,Fservices in the time ahead for which
OL,10,Fwe will need the expertise of our
OL,11,Fstaff."
OL,13,FNipsa, the largest union representing
OL,14,Fcivil servants in Northern Ireland,
OL,15,Fsaid it was recommending the offer to
OL,16,Fits members.
